function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	
--Spawn Alpha Werewolf
Hydra.ActorEnable(SPN_ALPHA)	
	
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)

--Alpha unattackable Entrance and howl
Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActorSpawned, false)
Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idActorSpawned, true)
Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idActorSpawned, false)
Hydra.Wait(2.5)
Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActorSpawned, true)
Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idActorSpawned, false)
Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idActorSpawned, true)
Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idActorSpawned, "Unstoppable_Monster")
Hydra.ActorPlaySound(idActorSpawned, SFX_HOWL)

--Spawn Stealth Werewolves and Progress Event
Hydra.ActorEnable(SPN_WERES)
Hydra.EventSendToActor("QST_Scos_Moors_WerewolfAmbush_Start", idSelf, idSelf)
Hydra.EventSend("QST_Scos_Moors_WerewolfAmbush_NafainWolf", idSelf)
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)

--Play stealth effect on spawned werewolves
Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idActorSpawned, EFF_STEALTH)
Hydra.ActorSetBloody(idActorSpawned, 0.5)

end
